@here per Family Leadership chat, we’ve been discussing the value in having the revive ability unlocked and maximised in one of our factions, or footing the bill should we need to procure revivers. A few things that were mentioned (for TL;DR);

1) The market for Revive contracts has been nerfed.
2) We presently pay into an AK fund to cover revives needed for AK purposes.
3) HBM have offered us their revive services.
4) A new faction warfare system is looming and may reignite the revive contract market.
5) If we’re going to be more aggressive (our own volition or system change) it would be beneficial to have our own revivers we can depend on. 

Please vote in favour or against having an in-house reviving function by using ✅ or ❎ reactions to this post.
